name: Jamboel bar
address: Jl. Wangsean - Klungah, Wismakerta, Kec. Sidemen, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80864, Indonesia
review 1: Jambul set up a tour for me and my dad to see the Baktur volcano. His colleague Solin drove us and he was an excellent driver. We had an excellent day and will never forget the experience. Afterwards he invited me to his bar where we sang karaoke and had some drinks. He makes a special pineapple cocktail that was very delicious!
review 2: Nice bar with delicious cocktail, in jamboel bar you can doing karaoke, with nice people, jamboel is a great person, if you in bali you must visit this place
review 3: Best bar I have ever been to, if bars had michlen stars this place would be a 3. Go to sideman and  come meet Jambul and sing at his bar and have a great time.
review 4: We had a great time visiting Jambul bar. The owner Jamboel is a super nice and friendly guy we will remember forever! Everyone in the area should definitely visit the bar for a great night!
review 5: Great bar! We had Jambul as our tour guide and talked about beer and he invited us. Later that evening we showed up and there were alot of local people. He introduced us and made us local drinks. He is a really good guide, host and karaoke singer. Yes, theres karaoke and its alot of fun. 10/10 would recommend
